  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Xfce4 Keyboard Plugin</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Xfce4 Keyboard Plugin</application> by running the
      following  
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr                --disable-debug              --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> :
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

